overview:
iTalkworld Provides Low Cost International Calls ,Cheap Calls from Computer , Mobile Apps & Access Numbers. A single account solves both the purposes , when you are in wifi or 3 G range , simply make calls through Computer or Mobile App via Internet , it does not use your Mobile Minutes . When not in Wi-fi or 3 G Range .. no problem simply Dial Access number if available in your country and simply place a call , you can choose to setup pinless Dialing . All Accounts include Free Voice mail & Free iNum Numbers , so iTalkworld user sitting anywhere in world can be reached from Google Talk or Google voice & also from Access Numbers in over 50 countries. Choose from pay per minute plan or monthly plans and call at Lowest rates. iTalkWorld also Provides Incoming Local Virtual Numbers from over 65 Countries with free incoming calls anywhere in world on our PC or Mobile apps , Forward calls to any number anywhere in world.

Incoming Virtual Numbers also called DID or Worldwide Number helps to get Local Presence in any of 65 + countries. eg : a person sitting in Germany can get a UK Number from any city and answer all calls on our Pc or Mobile App for Free , Further one can also setup call forwarding to any regular Landline or Mobile Phone , so you are always reachable . This makes a person always be local to everyone in UK , same applies to other countries where we offer Virtual Numbers.
